<section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-tag">// 01</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
            <div class="section-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-text">
                <p class="about-intro">Xin chào! Mình là <strong>Thi Tan Thinh</strong> (aka <strong>3tee</strong>) — một <strong>System Administrator</strong> và <strong>Platform Engineer</strong> đang làm việc tại Sacombank, chuyên vận hành digital banking trên Red Hat OpenShift.</p>
                <p>Mình có kinh nghiệm quản lý Kubernetes/OpenShift clusters trên RHEL, triển khai CI/CD, xây dựng observability stack (Prometheus, Elasticsearch, APM), và migrate legacy banking applications sang nền tảng hiện đại.</p>
                <p>Tốt nghiệp ngành <strong>Computer Networking and Data Communications</strong> tại <strong>UIT (ĐH Công nghệ Thông tin)</strong>. Triết lý làm việc: <em>"Automate everything, monitor everything, and keep production stable."</em></p>
                <div class="about-highlights">
                    <div class="highlight-item">
                        <span class="highlight-icon">🔧</span>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Container Platform</strong>
                            <span>OpenShift, Kubernetes, Docker</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="highlight-item">
                        <span class="highlight-icon">☁️</span>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Enterprise Middleware</strong>
                            <span>IBM MQ, Redis Enterprise, JBoss</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="highlight-item">
                        <span class="highlight-icon">📊</span>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Observability</strong>
                            <span>Prometheus, Elasticsearch, APM</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="highlight-item">
                        <span class="highlight-icon">🐧</span>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Linux & OS</strong>
                            <span>RHEL, CentOS, Ubuntu</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="about-terminal">
                <div class="mini-terminal">
                    <div class="mini-terminal-header">
                        <div class="terminal-dots">
                            <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
                            <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
                            <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
                        </div>
                        <span>system_info.sh</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mini-terminal-body">
                        <pre><code><span class="t-comment">#!/bin/bash</span>
<span class="t-command">echo</span> <span class="t-string">"=== System Engineer Profile ==="</span>

<span class="t-variable">NAME</span>=<span class="t-string">"Thi Tan Thinh"</span>
<span class="t-variable">ALIAS</span>=<span class="t-string">"3tee / just3tee"</span>
<span class="t-variable">ROLE</span>=<span class="t-string">"System Admin @ Sacombank"</span>
<span class="t-variable">LOCATION</span>=<span class="t-string">"Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam"</span>

<span class="t-comment"># Core competencies</span>
<span class="t-variable">SKILLS</span>=(<span class="t-string">"RHEL"</span> <span class="t-string">"OpenShift"</span> <span class="t-string">"K8s"</span>
    <span class="t-string">"IBM MQ"</span> <span class="t-string">"Redis"</span>
    <span class="t-string">"Prometheus"</span> <span class="t-string">"ELK"</span>)

<span class="t-comment"># Current status</span>
<span class="t-variable">CERTS</span>=<span class="t-string">"4x Red Hat Certified"</span>
<span class="t-variable">COFFEE_LEVEL</span>=<span class="t-string">"████████░░ 80%"</span>
<span class="t-variable">INCIDENTS_TODAY</span>=<span class="t-string">"0 🎉"</span>

<span class="t-command">echo</span> <span class="t-string">"Status: <span class="t-green">OPERATIONAL</span>"</span></code></pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
